Work Name Rough Translation (English): Khanisumurimar No. of Sarjapur village of Anekal Assembly constituency: 553 and 610 in bridge wall construction around Khabasthan (cemetery).

Work Name Rough Translation (English): Cement Road works from Maramma Temple at Basaveshwara temple in Lingarpur village of Harakadde Panchayat range of Anekal assembly constituency.
